full A_HREF_TO_REMOVE		/href[3D=\s\"\']*\S+(?:unsubscribe|remove)/i
describe A_HREF_TO_REMOVE	Link to a URL containing "remove"

full MAILTO_LINK		/=[3D=\s"']*mailto:/is
